&lt;p&gt;On July 18th, 2023, as the sound of the Amtrak horn echoed through Springfield train station, I picked up my bags and embarked on the long-awaited adventure of my life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why do I post these story one year later?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;A: While traveling, my mind was filled with countless stories and new experiences, and I could only capture them by jotting notes on my phone. Now that Iâ€™ve built my own blog and returned to the normal rhythm of life, I finally have a place to share these memories and reflect on them. More importantly, this journey reminds me to keep exploring the world, even as I step into new chapters or settle into an â€œordinaryâ€ life. I will continue working hard and learning from the world, again and again.&lt;/p&gt;
